snippet.title: Pac-Man World Re-Pac - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the Pac-Man World Re-Pac announcement trailer. Adventure to Ghost Island in remastered classic, Pac-Man World Re-Pac.

Pac-Man World Re-Pac releases on August 26, 2022 on PC, PS5, Xbox Series X|S, PS4, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #PacMan
